Lion DAO Genesis. Invoking special benevolent energy to those who own it. Elevating collective consciousness. 
These NFTs have been crafted with intention and are ready for our community to shape their future in the interoperable metaverse. All Lions & Lionesses hold potent royal codes which also serve as your immutable membership to Lion DAO. The opportunity to co-create a world of exclusive experiences, opportunities, and surprises. Part of Highvibe Network.
